did.unittitle: United Brotherhood of Carpenters and Joiners of America District Council Seattle records
did.abstract: Administrative papers of a city-wide coordinating body for affiliated local unions

bioghist.p: City-wide coordinating body for affiliated local unions. Along with the Carpenters and Joiners of America, the organizations included in this accession are the Central Labor Council of Seattle and Vicinity, Northwest Chapter of Associated General Contractors of America, Seattle Department of Lighting, and Washington State Council of the United Brotherhood of Carpenters and Joiners of America.
